							<div align="center">
								<font color="#880000" face="Comic Sans MS" size="6"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2">Ahoy Ye Swab's!</kw></font></div>
							<div align="left">
								<p><font color="#000011" face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Avast thar matey's and welcome. Look at that one-legged pirate. He be kind of scary to me.</kw><br>
										<br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">
										
									What thinks ye when ye hear the word PIRATES - adventures at sea searching for treasure chests of gold, walking the plank, and robbing other ships of valuables?&nbsp; </kw></font></p>
								<p><font color="#000011" face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Did ye know that thar were all kinds of pirates, even women.&nbsp; Are ye prepared to spy on a pirate on one of his blood thirsty adventures at sea?&nbsp; If so - What're ye watin fer? Let's hoist anchor and set sail. ARRRRR!</kw><br>
									</font></p>
							</div>
						</td>
