						<div align="left">
							<p><font color="#880000" face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2">PART 1:</kw></font><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3"> Wait, if you don't want to "Walk the Plank" you better find out more about pirates before we begin our voyage. In fact, why don't you pretend you were alive when pirates roamed the Caribbean. Explore the links below. Then fill out the "If I Was a Pirate Sheet". Captain 
                            Hamlin will give you the sheet to use while you explore these sites. After you become a pirate we can cast off and go on our voyage. </kw></font><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="3"><img src="images/Map.jpg" alt="" align="right" border="0" vspace="20" width="264" height="239" hspace="45"></font></p>
						</div>
						<p><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><a href="Pages/General/pirates.html"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Pirates: What's in a  Name?</kw></a></font></p>
						<p><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><a href="Pages/ships/Ship.html"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Pirate Ships</kw></a></font></p>
						<p><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><a href="Pages/Weapons/weapons.html"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Pirate Weapons</kw></a></font></p>
