						<center>
							<p></p>
							<hr width="75%" noshade="noshade">
							<p><font color="#880000" face="Comic Sans MS" size="5"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2">Part 2: The Voyage</kw></font></p>
						</center>
						<div align="left">
							<p><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Let's get started. While on this adventure you will create a "Wanted Poster" for a pirate you learned about on your voyage.&nbsp; The poster will include a clip art picture of the pirate you choose, with a </kw><img src="images/pirate_standing.jpg" alt="" align="left" border="0" width="230" height="395"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">listing of his/her crimes and any reward that will be offered.</kw><br>
									<br>
								</font><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">You will use Microsoft Publisher software to make and print the poster.</kw><br>
									<br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">
									To spy on the pirate you choose, follow the steps below to be successful.</kw></font><font color="#aa0000" face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><i><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3"> But be careful that the pirate doesn't capture YOU!&nbsp;</kw></i></font><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3"> While spying on your pirate you need to think about these questions: </kw><br>
									<br>
								</font><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">1. What is he/she is famous for?&nbsp;</kw><br>
									<br>
								</font><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">2. What type of crimes did the pirate commit during his/her lifetime?&nbsp;</kw><br>
									<br>
								</font><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">The "Wanted Poster" must be your design, so be as creative as you want to be. When the posters are finished they will be displayed in the hallway for other classes to see.</kw></font></p>
						</div>
						<div align="center">
							<hr width="50%" noshade="noshade">
							<font color="#880000" face="Comic Sans MS" size="5"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2">Spying on Pirates </kw></font></div>
						<div align="left">
							<p><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Most of the famous pirates sailed in the Caribbean Sea shown</kw><a href="images/Map.gif"><img src="images/Mapt.gif" alt="" align="right" border="0" vspace="10" width="73" height="91" hspace="10"></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3"> in this picture of a map. Click on this picture to see a larger map. ---&gt;</kw></font></p>
							<p><font face="Comic Sans MS" size="4"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">Now look at all priate links below and decide which pirate to choose for your poster. Then you can go back and collect the information needed for your WANTED POSTER.</kw></font></p>
						</div>
